{"word":"ἴφθιμος","slug":"ἴφθιμος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n51424\" key=\"i)/fqimos\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἴφθῑμος</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">η</itype>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ον</itype>, also <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ος</itype>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ον</itype> (v. infr.), <sense id=\"n51424.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">stout, strong</tr_>, of bodily strength, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὤμοις ἰ</foreign>. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:18:204\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">18.204</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">κρατὶ ἐπ᾽ ἰ</foreign>. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:3:336\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.336</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἰ. ποταμῶν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:17:749\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">17.749</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">βοῶν ἴ. κάρηνα</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:23:260\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">23.260</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; of heroes, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἴ. ψυχαί, κεφαλαί</foreign>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:3\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.3</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:11:55\" default=